<section class="min-h-screen px-4 sm:px-6 py-6 sm:py-10" style="--theme-primary: {{#if isOngDashboard}}#6B8F71{{else}}#4886D9{{/if}}; --theme-strong: {{#if isOngDashboard}}#2F3E34{{else}}#2D4BA6{{/if}}; --theme-soft: {{#if isOngDashboard}}#EAF3EC{{else}}#DBEAFE{{/if}};">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-[#102235] border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-sm text-center">
      <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto rounded-2xl bg-[var(--theme-soft)] dark:bg-[var(--theme-primary)]/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-7 h-7 text-[var(--theme-strong)] dark:text-[var(--theme-soft)]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414A1 1 0 0119 9.414V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 dark:text-white/40 mb-2">
        Transparencia indisponivel
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
        Esta ONG ainda nao possui documentacao aprovada.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-white/60 mt-3 leading-relaxed">
        A pagina de transparencia fica disponivel somente depois que a equipe administrativa aprova os documentos da ONG.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-7 flex justify-center">
        <a href="/ongs"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-5 py-3 rounded-xl bg-[var(--theme-primary)] hover:bg-[var(--theme-strong)] text-white text-sm font-semibold transition">
          Voltar para explorar ONGs
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
